name: Mieruko-chan Miko Yotsuya

Miko Yotsuya from Mieruko-chan (見える子ちゃん, "The Girl Who Can See Them")

A girl with balls of steel

Default weight: 1. Default look: yellow sweater, school uniform, black tie

Alternatives:
